      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://blogs.susankhanal.com/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blogs.susankhanal.com/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi, I&amp;rsquo;m &lt;strong&gt;Susan Khanal&lt;/strong&gt; — an IT and networking enthusiast building and breaking things in my homelab.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This blog is where I document everything I learn: network setups, self-hosted services, Linux configs, firewalls, and anything else I experiment with.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-youll-find-here&#34;&gt;What you&amp;rsquo;ll find here&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Step-by-step homelab tutorials with real screenshots&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Networking deep-dives (VLANs, DNS, VPNs)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Self-hosted app setups (Proxmox, Docker, Kubernetes)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;IT study notes and certification prep&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;my-setup&#34;&gt;My setup&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hypervisor&lt;/strong&gt;: Vmware ESXi 8&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Switching&lt;/strong&gt;: Managed VLAN switches&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DNS&lt;/strong&gt;: Adguard + Unbound&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;connect&#34;&gt;Connect&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Got questions or found an error? Reach out — I&amp;rsquo;m always learning.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
